{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01GZZqeohvXub99M9AcUKQ7V","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The 3-node CockroachDB cluster is fully deployed and healthy. Summary of what was created:\n\n- **Service `crdb-cluster`** — headless (ClusterIP: None), exposing grpc/26257 and http/8080, selecting on both required labels\n- **Service `crdb-cluster-public`** — standard ClusterIP service on the same ports\n- **StatefulSet `crdb-cluster`** — 3 replicas, image `cockroachdb/cockroach:v24.1.0`, `podManagementPolicy: Parallel` (needed so all 3 nodes start simultaneously before init), 10Gi PVC per pod\n- **PodDisruptionBudget** — `minAvailable: 2` to preserve quorum during voluntary disruptions\n- All pods carry labels `app.kubernetes.io/name: cockroachdb` and `app.kubernetes.io/instance: crdb-cluster`\n\nThe key issue resolved: StatefulSet's default sequential pod creation caused a deadlock (pod 0 needed the other nodes to pass `health?ready=1`), fixed by switching to `Parallel` pod management and running `cockroach init` once all nodes were up."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":491,"cache_read_input_tokens":36787,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":491},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"94e634c6-7de0-481f-bea8-c899d3d6850e","uuid":"c90f6657-138d-447c-8d45-3fe61cedb90c","request_id":"req_011CcfB8i1YLSYCoo6JVVBan"}
